# blette

A toolbox for edge detection tasks (binary and multi-label edges).

## Installation

```Bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

# global package
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

- [Cityscapes](./.readme/cityscapes.md)
- [BSDS500](./.readme/bsds500.md)
